The Sage 
	Character for Slay The Spire

A mechanic who studied about the cult of a blue bird.
She learned flying a carpet and brewing potions in order to stop its rise.

Starts with 50 HP, 169 gold	

**STARTING RELIC**
	Flying Carpet
		At the start of your second turn, 1 Flight. 

**STARTING DECK**
   4x Strike
		Attack, 1 Energy: 
		Deal 6 (9) damage.
	4x Defend
		Skill, 1 Energy: 
		Gain 5 (8) Block.
	1x Bold move
		Attack, 0 Energy:
		Deal 6 (9) damage. Gain 2 Frail.
	1x Fly
		Skill, 2 (1) Energy: 
		If you don't fly, gain 1 Flight.

